1
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:01,880
Well, take whatever you like.

2
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:02,680
It's on me.

3
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,239
We just came in to get out of the rain.

4
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,560
Why buy flowers?

5
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:07,980
This is for you.

6
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,600
Don't get the wrong idea.

7
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,560
I just felt coming into this shop

8
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,240
and not picking anything is awkward.

9
00:01:13,240 --> 00:01:13,720
Here.

10
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,440
What's going on?

11
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,450
Are you allergic to pollen?

12
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,340
Why didn't you say so earlier?

13
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:27,130
I just found out myself.

14
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:29,480
Don't tell me

15
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,460
no man has ever given you flowers.

16
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:34,720
You...

17
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,759
I have always received gold bars.

18
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,720
Who is as stingy as you?

19
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:40,759
Ouch, ouch, ouch.

20
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,759
Donate 5%

21
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,680
to support animal protection.

22
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,400
Are you crazy?

23
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,920
This is Su Wan's project, right?

24
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,500
You're being ridiculous.

25
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,420
I just want to discuss it with you.

26
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,039
After all, it's not a bad thing, right?

27
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,759
Right, Dad?

28
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,400
Dad, talk to him.

29
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,160
I think it's good.

30
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:17,570
Everyone is responsible for helping stray animals.

31
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,200
Then I'll sign it.

32
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,160
You're a hopeless romantic.

33
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,440
Keep it a secret.

34
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,040
I can't.

35
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,720
I have a big mouth.

36
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,440
Beg me.

37
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,079
I'm so sorry.

38
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,079
I'm late. Sorry.

39
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,040
It's okay. Sit.

40
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,020
How did you know today is my birthday?

41
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:32,079
This is a surprise I prepared.

42
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,240
A surprise?

43
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,280
I made it myself.

44
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,240
You are so amazing.

45
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,800
You can race and repair cars.

46
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,210
And you even make cakes.

47
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,530
Have a taste.

48
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,720
This is so cute.

49
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,160
Is this little girl me?

50
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,800
Yes, it's you.

51
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,040
The candles are so pretty.

52
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,700
Make a wish.

53
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,600
Come on.

54
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,720
I hope we can be happy every day.

55
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:21,680
I hope he can spend many birthdays with me.

56
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,450
Happy birthday.

57
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,040
What I want to say is,

58
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:42,159
whether you are sad or happy in the future,

59
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:45,840
I will always be by your side.

60
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,720
Actually, to me,

61
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,740
as long as you are here,

62
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:56,240
every day is the happiest.

63
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,720
Oh, right.

64
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,000
And this.

65
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,970
What is this?

66
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,320
Su Wan, you caused such a big mess.

67
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,450
Come home right now.

68
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,880
What is it? Why the rush?

69
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,240
Sorry, Tianyu.

70
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,260
I have an emergency and have to go.

71
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,280
I'll take this with me.

72
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,560
Take the cake back and eat it.

73
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,360
I have an emergency. I have to go.

74
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:26,360
Then... Then...

75
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,800
Where are you going? Let me take you.

76
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,860
It's fine. No need.

77
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,480
I'll explain it to you later.

78
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,159
Big news! Big news!

79
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,400
Something big happened at our school.

80
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,120
Everyone,

81
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,760
Did you check the school forum?

82
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:41,159
Abusing animals under the guise of protecting them.

83
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:44,240
I heard the president of that animal association is named Su Wan.

84
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,770
This person is so inhumane.

85
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,440
People like this will get punished sooner or later.

86
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,000
We must kick her out of Lucheng University.

87
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,960
Get out here now, you involved party!

88
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,680
Su Wan.

89
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,700
It seems they adopted animals

90
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,720
for abusive experiments.

91
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:27,080
You said Sister Su Wan is the president of the Animal Association.

92
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:27,760
Could it be...

93
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,360
She wouldn't do such a thing.

94
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:33,080
But Sister Su Wan really has psychological issues.

95
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:36,920
And didn't she cause the death of...

96
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:40,010
Don't talk nonsense, little girl.

97
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,840
My sister is perfectly fine.

98
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,500
She likes animals so much.

99
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,540
Impossible, impossible.

100
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,720
But,

101
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,840
if others believe this is true,

102
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,200
what should we do?

103
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,120
There must be something wrong with this.

104
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,850
I will find evidence to prove Su Wan's innocence.

105
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,920
Doudou, wake up.

106
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,880
Don't scare me.

107
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:27,960
Doudou.

108
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:28,600
Dou...

109
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,280
Don't.

110
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:31,520
Don't.

111
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:13,600
Su Wan,

112
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,320
the food is ready.

113
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,730
Come out and eat.

114
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,080
Su Wan,

115
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,440
can you come out?

116
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,520
Su Wan,

117
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,360
come out.

118
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,120
How is it? Still not answering?

119
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,580
Don't be discouraged.

120
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,440
Dad, I'm going out.

121
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,200
Okay.

122
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,360
Su Wan is inside.

123
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:05,920
Su Wan.

124
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,560
Su Wan.

125
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,250
Brother.

126
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,320
If I had known Su Wan would cause you so much trouble,

127
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,980
on her first day at the garage,

128
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,850
I would have kicked her out.

129
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,640
Brother.

130
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,440
Is it necessary to go this far for Su Wan?

131
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,640
It's one thing to neglect the store's business,

132
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,480
but you also spend money everywhere gathering information.

133
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,540
What are you after?

134
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,570
This matter,

135
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,360
you didn't do it, did you?

136
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,640
You suspect me?

137
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,320
It's fine if you favor Su Wan,

138
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,040
but don't slander my sister.

139
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,500
Give me your phone.

140
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,250
Brother.

141
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,120
Give it to me.

142
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,200
What is this?
